     <h2>Discover the Difference Between International Education and Global Learning</h2> 
     <p>Weâ€™ve developed a unique cycle of global learning for our own programs to help you make the most of your cross-cultural experiences. Youâ€™ll spend a semester studying the region before you leave. While youâ€™re there, Westmont professors will guide your learning. When you return, a re-entry seminar will help you embrace, apply and share your insights.</p> 
     <p>Westmont prepares you to be a global citizen equipped to make an impact in the world. About <strong>70 percent</strong> of our students spend a semester off campus or overseas, choosing from <strong>more than 65 programs</strong>.</p> 
